  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to find the optimum radiation dose and number of cycles for an ABVD
      chemotherapy combined with an involved field irradiation. It is to be tested whether the
      reduction from 4 to 2 cycles of ABVD and/or the reduction of the radiation dose from 30 to 20
      Gy is feasible without a loss of efficacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
